{"tid":1790092,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【無良租客】全屋發霉曱甴屍 日本房東: 絕對不再租給外國人","createTime":"2019-12-19T17:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T03:07:56.000Z","uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d123ddadfee5fc4b25671cdf4881a68e46359b58","tid":1790092,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/lijpg.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C-6.png?w=593&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Flijpg.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%25A1%258C-6.png%3Fw%3D593%26ssl%3D1&h=03c8f7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本網民ジャムおじ(笑屋)日前在twitter發文， 表示絕對不會再租房給外國人，並上載多張房間的室內照，可見相片中的房間長滿黑霉，滿地都是曱甴死屍，相信是該名租客的所仍所為。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/lijpg.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C2-1.png?w=602&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Flijpg.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%25A1%258C2-1.png%3Fw%3D602%26ssl%3D1&h=57270b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該名網民又表示，「租客可以也有點罪惡感，退租前故意留下曱甴屋，要不然曱甴現今還在房內活蹦亂跳。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/lijpg.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/%E7%84%A1%E9%A1%8C3-1.png?w=578&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Flijpg.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E9%25A1%258C3-1.png%3Fw%3D578%26ssl%3D1&h=e7915a80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n該房東表示，租客是尼泊爾或越南人，租期長達2年。<br />\n<br />\n其他網民看到貼文後都表示，以後租房給外國人時會加倍小心。<br />\n由於筆者本人也是在日本默默耕耘的一名外國人，真不希望有人做壞風氣，連累他人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民反應<br />\n<br />\n9: イオ(東京都) [CA] 2019/12/17(火) 10:50:13.77 ID:q+H7GJPS0<br />\n要怎樣才能弄成這副慘狀&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n10: アクルックス(茸) [US] 2019/12/17(火) 10:50:18.67 ID:XWZlqHGx0<br />\n肯定是在家中不穿鞋赤腳生活<br />\n<br />\n11: エイベル2218(広島県) [US] 2019/12/17(火) 10:50:35.03 ID:nrEoczjO0<br />\n就算每天在浴室小便也不會變成這樣吧<br />\n<br />\n15: ダークエネルギー(鹿児島県) [ﾆﾀﾞ] 2019/12/17(火) 10:52:27.57 ID:npqxeMTn0 家居清潔公司要頭痛了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n26: 北アメリカ星雲(福岡県) [PL] 2019/12/17(火) 10:57:18.74 ID:rDSnUpWj0<br />\n外國人退租後只要逃回家鄉便沒有任何後果，所以最好還是不要租房給外國人<br />\n<br />\n30: ウンブリエル(東京都) [NO] 2019/12/17(火) 10:58:24.50 ID:Hgq4yuS20<br />\n所以租給外國人前一定要收保證金<br />\n<br />\n56: 天王星(茸) [ﾆﾀﾞ] 2019/12/17(火) 11:06:13.98 ID:rlsupbb70<br />\n本以為黑色點的發霉，放大一看原來是小強，嚇死了<br />\n<br />\n71: デネボラ(大阪府) [US] 2019/12/17(火) 11:10:47.00 ID:Zl17pQcC0<br />\n正常人退租前會打掃一下吧&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n188: バン・アレン帯(家) [US] 2019/12/17(火) 12:12:46.98 ID:aHGyv27m0<br />\n髒到連蟑螂也生存不了&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n320: ベテルギウス(東京都) [PT] 2019/12/17(火) 16:11:56.14 ID:9BORo2Rr0<br />\n外國人經常在晚上叫朋友到家中開派對，很困擾<br />\n<br />\n325: プレアデス星団(東京都) [US] 2019/12/17(火) 16:53:30.95 ID:pcm0Tfe70<br />\n租房給亞洲土人的話，最後會變成10個人住一間房，他們又不打掃，真是可怕<br />\n<br />\n339: 環状星雲(ジパング) [GB] 2019/12/17(火) 18:31:19.00 ID:GFmneXUz0<br />\n正常人在變成這副慘狀前會先忍耐不住，打掃衛生吧<br />\n<br />\n原文:<a href=\"https://lijpg.com/?p=272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flijpg.com%2F%3Fp%3D272&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Xr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=e3f4b7d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lijpg.com/?p=272</a>"},{"pid":"43b9eafaa175c8542da8149daed3fa43b1665471","tid":1790092,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f4da2dcf3550cdf11d67bc1a225faea9c8194713","tid":1790092,"uid":181675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"估錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2450b4c44727c0f68fd7dda783dcbd6c9704c39","tid":1790092,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:17:26.000Z","msg":"唔夠租霸咁惡"},{"pid":"69e569787c7ab860eac3f4bc646289a87217460c","tid":1790092,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco