.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1855baea8045b62a2af44765c89affb1b7af7028","tid":1790092,"uid":210669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:04:03.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe916a07eee9a09157ee8e1cc1c458065e9e5e24","tid":1790092,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"對比香港好似好普通"}]}